OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776243304
OL,3,CEasyJet passenger stranded in Milan
OL,4,Cfor four days after EU border chaos
OL,6,FAn easyJet customer has told ITV News
OL,7,Fshe missed her flight home from Milan
OL,8,Fdue to EU border chaos despite
OL,9,Farriving at the airport four hours
OL,10,Fearly.
OL,12,FLily-Mae Bridgehouse, from Oldham, is
OL,13,Famong the more than 100 passengers who
OL,14,Fdidn't make their flight to Manchester
OL,15,Fon Sunday because of long queues at
OL,16,Fpassport control in Milan Linate
OL,17,FAirport.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776243304
OL,3,CEasyJet passenger stranded in Milan
OL,4,Cfor four days after EU border chaos
OL,6,FThe 23-year-old, who was flying alone
OL,7,Ffor the first time, said she was
OL,8,Fforced to take four days of unpaid
OL,9,Fleave as a result of the cancellation.
OL,10,FThe next available flight only leaves
OL,11,Fon Thursday.
OL,13,FIt comes as travellers face big delays
OL,14,Fand long queues at some airports in
OL,15,FEurope following the implementation of
OL,16,Fthe EU's new Entry/Exit system (EES).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776243304
OL,3,CEasyJet passenger stranded in Milan
OL,4,Cfor four days after EU border chaos
OL,6,FThe system, which replaces passport
OL,7,Fstamps with biometric checks, is
OL,8,Fdesigned to be more efficient, but
OL,9,Fteething issues are causing
OL,10,Ffrustration for many passengers trying
OL,11,Fto return to the UK.
OL,13,FMs Bridgehouse said she arrived at the
OL,14,Fairport four hours early and had
OL,15,Fplenty of time before her 10.30am
OL,16,Fflight was assigned a gate.
OL,18,FAt 9.30am, the flight had been
OL,19,Fassigned a gate number, and she was
OL,20,Ftold by a member of staff to join a
OL,21,Fqueue.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776243304
OL,3,CEasyJet passenger stranded in Milan
OL,4,Cfor four days after EU border chaos
OL,6,F"We were stood in the queue for about
OL,7,Fan hour and a half... probably even
OL,8,Flonger," she told ITV News, adding
OL,9,Fthat staff kept calling people for
OL,10,FLondon Gatwick and London Heathrow but
OL,11,Fnot for Manchester.
OL,13,FWhen Ms Bridgehouse and some other
OL,14,Fpassengers went to ask for updates,
OL,15,Fshe said staff told them: "Don't
OL,16,Fworry, it's not going to leave without
OL,17,Fyou, it will stay here until you all
OL,18,Fboard."
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776243304
OL,3,CEasyJet passenger stranded in Milan
OL,4,Cfor four days after EU border chaos
OL,6,FBut as the queue slowly budged
OL,7,Fforward, the flight was no longer
OL,8,Flisted on the departure board, she
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FShe said: "After about half an hour,
OL,12,Fwe asked again, saying, 'Why hasn't it
OL,13,Fgone on the board yet? Why haven't we
OL,14,Fgone through yet? It's about half 11,
OL,15,Fsurely we've missed the flight.
OL,17,F"She came back to us and said, 'It's
OL,18,Fgone, so I said, 'What do you mean
OL,19,Fit's gone? I need to be on that
OL,20,Fflight, I have work tomorrow I have
OL,21,Fkids I need to get home to'.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776243304
OL,3,CEasyJet passenger stranded in Milan
OL,4,Cfor four days after EU border chaos
OL,6,F"They said, 'There's nothing we can
OL,7,Fdo, it's gone, you need to come out of
OL,8,Fthe queue'".
OL,10,FMs Bridgehouse said she struggles with
OL,11,Fanxiety, making her ordeal all the
OL,12,Fmore difficult.
OL,14,FTravel expert Sally Gethin explains
OL,15,Fwhat travellers can do to protect
OL,16,Fthemselves during severe delays like
OL,17,Fthose in Milan on Sunday
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776243304
OL,3,CEasyJet passenger stranded in Milan
OL,4,Cfor four days after EU border chaos
OL,6,FShe said she started "getting really
OL,7,Fpanicky" when customers were led all
OL,8,Fthe way back through departures and
OL,9,Ftold to go down some stairs and
OL,10,Foutside, adding: "I was a mess. I was
OL,11,Fterrified."
OL,13,FPassengers were eventually ushered to
OL,14,Fan easyJet desk where they were handed
OL,15,Fa sheet of paper confirming that their
OL,16,Fflight had been cancelled, Ms
OL,17,FBridgehouse said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776243304
OL,3,CEasyJet passenger stranded in Milan
OL,4,Cfor four days after EU border chaos
OL,6,FThe earliest flight she could find to
OL,7,FManchester was four days later from
OL,8,FMilano Malpensa Airport, which she
OL,9,Fbooked.
OL,11,FHer partner was staying in Milan for
OL,12,Fbusiness, so she took a bus back into
OL,13,Fthe city to stay with him.
OL,15,FAfter a lengthy call with easyJet's
OL,16,Fcustomer service, she was told she'd
OL,17,Fhave to pay #52 to switch to the
OL,18,FThursday flight.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776243304
OL,3,CEasyJet passenger stranded in Milan
OL,4,Cfor four days after EU border chaos
OL,6,FHowever, she said that does not make
OL,7,Fup for the extra expenses she has
OL,8,Fincurred staying in Milan, nor the
OL,9,Ffour days of missed work for which her
OL,10,Femployer says it cannot pay her.
OL,12,FEasyJet told ITV News they have
OL,13,Freimbursed Ms Bridgehouse for the
OL,14,Fcancellation fee
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776243304
OL,3,CEasyJet passenger stranded in Milan
OL,4,Cfor four days after EU border chaos
OL,6,F"It's made me really nervous to
OL,7,Freturn, going to that new airport,
OL,8,Fbecause I'm thinking it's just going
OL,9,Fto happen all over again and I'm going
OL,10,Fto be stuck here even longer. It has
OL,11,Freally knocked my confidence," she
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,F"We just want someone to take
OL,15,Faccountability for it, apologise, and
OL,16,Fpromise that it's not going to happen
OL,17,Fagain, or that they're going to have
OL,18,Fthings in place moving forward to make
OL,19,Fit easier."
OL,26,@vD@AOU
